  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00072', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某國政府所推動的政策，為其他國家政府引入成為該政府推動之新政策。此一過程稱為： 政策競爭  政策擴散  漸進政策  政策賡續', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00073', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '依地方制度法規定，下列何者不屬於縣（市）自治事項？ 防洪排水設施興建管理   證券交易市場管理 殯葬設施之設置及管理   都市計畫之擬定', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00074', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '地方自治事項涉及跨直轄市、縣（市）、鄉（鎮、市）區域時，有關處理方式之敘述，下列何者錯誤？ 由各該地方自治團體協商辦理 共同上級業務主管機關沒有權限指定其中一個地方自治團體限期辦理 得經過地方民意機關通過後，設合辦事業組織經營之 得成立區域合作組織、訂定協議、行政契約或以其他方式合作', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00075', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關「第三方政府（the third party government）」的興起與功能，下列敘述何者錯誤？ 為薩拉門（L. Salamon）所提倡  企圖補足人民對公共服務的渴望 懼怕企業對資本市場的影響過大  市場失靈或政府失靈的現象', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00076', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '針對民間捐助之財團法人之經營管理，下列敘述何者正確？ 董事之間不得有配偶或三親等內親屬關係之情形 應設置董事會 董事之任期每屆不得逾3年 董事人數應為雙數', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00077', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關我國社會企業之敘述，何者錯誤？ 「喜憨兒社會福利基金會」的庇護工廠具有促進就業與服務提供的功能 以促進公益為主要使命，不以創造經濟價值為目標 政府補助為其收入來源之一 服務對象包括身心障礙、弱勢群體等', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('islands-e3452428-moex-00078', 'islands-e3452428', 'islands-e3452428-moex-114-4dccc0e6', 'sub-islands-e3452428-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「配合國家政策，由民間機構自行備具私有土地投資興建，擁有所有權，並自為營運或委託第三人營運」 的作法，屬於民辦民營中的那一種類型？ BOT（build-operate-transfer）  OT（operate-transfer） BTO（build-transfer-operate）  BOO（build-own-operate）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "06786d62fb55", "answer_pdf_sha1": "242e83f0aff7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114190", "c": "601", "s": "0512", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "行政學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試、離島地區公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "islands", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
